parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Corrosion of the front strut housing can cause the strut to fail, leading to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.

strut housing corrosion and perforation.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Rear suspension bottoming out can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
